sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator
    participant Script as recover_from_qdrant.py
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant Client
    participant FalkorDB as FalkorDB Connection
    
    Operator->>Script: Execute recovery
    Script->>Qdrant: Scroll all points<br/>qdrant_client.scroll()
    Qdrant-->>Script: Return 780 memories<br/>with full payloads
    
    loop For each memory
        Script->>Script: Extract fields from payload<br/>content, type, confidence, etc.
        Script->>Script: Filter metadata fields<br/>RESERVED_FIELDS blocklist
        Script->>FalkorDB: MERGE (m:Memory {id, content})<br/>SET m.type, m.confidence...
        Script->>FalkorDB: Extract relationships<br/>from metadata.relationships
        Script->>FalkorDB: CREATE edge patterns<br/>RELATES_TO, PREFERS_OVER, etc.
    end
    
    Script->>Script: Calculate stats<br/>memories, relationships, entities
    Script-->>Operator: Recovery complete<br/>778/780 recovered (99.7%)